{"tid":2283702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"靚女就好比一部林寶堅尼","createTime":"2020-11-12T19:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T06:08:23.000Z","uid":103799,"like":55,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5bebaf703ecd3097c461e6243de0643938353f0b","tid":2283702,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"林寶堅尼係比有實力有錢有地位嘅人渣<br />\n<br />\n如果自己唔係好有條件<br />\n何必一定要追女神<br />\n<br />\n追一部自己揸唔起買唔起嘅林寶堅尼?<br />\n之後揸唔起就罵部車貴罵貪錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實自己無條件<br />\n渣部錢七咪一樣得<br />\n<br />\n最緊要岩自己"},{"pid":"f6f2840016210f5421a6559920d5a70fe876618e","tid":2283702,"uid":324265,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"大部份靚女都係虛有其表 <br />\n林寶就外內兼備<br />\n所以 靚女\\=林寶<br />\n所以繼續痴漢d靚女係無問題 <br />\n終有一日可以食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林寶唔撚同 <br />\n無錢就真係買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077c094c3e2b37d4ee9623bb5351733a85cb908b","tid":2283702,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f6f2840016210f5421a6559920d5a70fe876618e","tid":2283702,"uid":324265,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"大部份靚女都係虛有其表 <br />\n林寶就外內兼備<br />\n所以 靚女\\=林寶<br />\n所以繼續痴漢d靚女係無問題 <br />\n終有一日可以食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林寶唔撚同 <br />\n無錢就真係買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T19:42:50.000Z","msg":"係真靚女就夠<br />\n男人要外表多於內在<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內在可以搵唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0c8a17440c8bb4b41e3956bdc6a983e92a31b5","tid":2283702,"uid":167177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:08:25.000Z","msg":"化起妝大把靚女<br />\n要有內涵數唔到幾多個係事實"},{"pid":"dd6b975be30167fe92074ff32f6606dd57602bf3","tid":2283702,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0c8a174